China, Japan Should Push Crisis Control, Ministry Says

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-10-23T11:09:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/china-japan-should-push-crisis-control-ministry-says-correct-.html
(Corrects that Tang is no longer state councilor.)  China and  Japan  should build and
develop maritime crisis control systems as part of measures to
prevent accidents at sea, according to a statement on the
Chinese Ministry of Foreign Affairs website today, citing former
State Councilor Tang Jiaxuan.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gregory Turk at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  